## How to invoke this skill

**Minimum prompt** (user can write only this):

```
Додай компонент [Name] за нашими скілами.
Figma: [https://figma.com/design/...?node-id=...]
```

**Optional additions:**

- «Тільки Фаза 1» / «тільки мапінг» — stop after mapping table
- «Без showcase» — Phases 1–2 only
- Variant names or UA copy preferences
- «Комітни після ОК» — only then run git commit/push

**Agent must:** load this rule + `prytula-design-system`, run phases in order, **halt at each STOP** until user replies **ОК** (or equivalent).

**Example (user):**

```
Додай компонент DonateButton за нашими скілами.
Figma: https://www.figma.com/design/hiAQiy4aRZQiwD1S4jekxY/Prytula-Responsive?node-id=123-456
```

**Example (agent after Phase 1):** structure + mapping table → wait.  
**After Phase 2:** files + `DonateButton.tsx` → wait.  
**After Phase 3:** `DonateButtonShowcase.tsx`, `routes.tsx` diff + commit message → wait.
